  "instructions": [
    "Heat the rendered pork fat in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped celery and cook until it is tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken broth, shio koji, and salt to the pot, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Cook the ramen noodles according to the package instructions and set aside.",
    "Add the cooked noodles to the pot and stir to combine.",
    "Drizzle the sesame oil over the top and sprinkle with chopped green onions.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
